00:04:39.170 --> 00:04:40.760 align:middle line:10%
>>I'm a writer.

00:04:40.760 --> 00:04:44.120 align:middle line:10%
For me, inspiration
is essential.

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:46.500 align:middle line:90%
Creativity is essential.

00:04:46.500 --> 00:04:49.640 align:middle line:84%
And I can only find
