00:26:25.880 --> 00:26:27.100 align:middle line:90%
I can laugh at it now.

00:26:27.100 --> 00:26:30.200 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, who is
this me, or I, or self?

00:26:30.200 --> 00:26:34.190 align:middle line:84%
What is it in religion, or
in spiritual traditions,

00:26:34.190 --> 00:26:35.820 align:middle line:90%
or in philosophy?

00:26:35.820 --> 00:26:37.940 align:middle line:90%
What is it?

00:26:37.940 --> 00:26:40.580 align:middle line:84%
>>Every spiritual tradition
throughout history

00:26:40.580 --> 00:26:44.480 align:middle line:84%
has spoken about the heart as
being the seed of the soul.

00:26:44.480 --> 00:26:47.690 align:middle line:10%
The diamond in the heart,
the lotus and the heart,

00:26:47.690 --> 00:26:50.000 align:middle line:10%
the temple in the heart.

00:26:50.000 --> 00:26:52.610 align:middle line:10%
Every tradition
speaks about the heart

00:26:52.610 --> 00:26:57.190 align:middle line:10%
as being the essence
of who we are.

00:26:57.190 --> 00:27:02.200 align:middle line:84%
>>The heart points to the most
essential dimension within you.

00:27:02.200 --> 00:27:05.250 align:middle line:84%
So to live in
connectedness with that,

00:27:05.250 --> 00:27:09.310 align:middle line:84%
then you are in touch with
the power of the heart, which

00:27:09.310 --> 00:27:14.260 align:middle line:90%
is the power of life itself.

00:27:14.260 --> 00:27:17.560 align:middle line:84%
The power of the
very intelligence

00:27:17.560 --> 00:27:23.230 align:middle line:84%
that pervades and underlies
the entire universe.

00:27:23.230 --> 00:27:26.800 align:middle line:84%
>>Divine intelligence
is in your heart.

00:27:26.800 --> 00:27:30.060 align:middle line:84%
You will not find your
soul in your intellect.

00:27:30.060 --> 00:27:33.470 align:middle line:84%
>>And I suddenly thought,
wow, look at all these notes.

00:27:33.470 --> 00:27:35.580 align:middle line:90%
This could be a magazine.

00:27:35.580 --> 00:27:39.596 align:middle line:84%
And the title was easy, because
it made me really happy.

00:27:39.596 --> 00:27:40.580 align:middle line:90%
Happiness.

00:27:40.580 --> 00:28:01.260 align:middle line:90%


00:28:01.260 --> 00:28:05.900 align:middle line:84%
So to listen to your heart
can be very frightening,

00:28:05.900 --> 00:28:09.110 align:middle line:84%
because you might have to lose
all the secure things that life

00:28:09.110 --> 00:28:14.210 align:middle line:84%
was giving you, like cars,
money, houses, everything.

00:28:14.210 --> 00:28:17.610 align:middle line:84%
>>Well, I'm a person
who has a lot of fear.

00:28:17.610 --> 00:28:21.110 align:middle line:84%
Like for example,
every time that I

00:28:21.110 --> 00:28:23.960 align:middle line:90%
have to write a new book.

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:27.600 align:middle line:84%
Would I be able
to express myself?

00:28:27.600 --> 00:28:30.340 align:middle line:84%
Would I be able
to share my soul?

00:28:30.340 --> 00:28:33.870 align:middle line:84%
>>When we consider
challenging fear,

00:28:33.870 --> 00:28:37.620 align:middle line:84%
we're actually considering
shining the light of awareness

00:28:37.620 --> 00:28:40.830 align:middle line:84%
on those places within
us that are fearful.

00:28:40.830 --> 00:28:43.180 align:middle line:84%
>>There is nothing
wrong with fear.

00:28:43.180 --> 00:28:47.340 align:middle line:84%
The only thing that is wrong
is to be paralyzed by fear.

00:28:47.340 --> 00:28:51.960 align:middle line:84%
>>So I thought, OK, I face
it, I just face it, this fear.

00:28:51.960 --> 00:28:56.180 align:middle line:84%
What will happen to me if this
magazine is not a success?

00:28:56.180 --> 00:28:58.252 align:middle line:90%
Maybe I have to sell the house.

00:28:58.252 --> 00:28:59.460 align:middle line:90%
So I looked to another house.

00:28:59.460 --> 00:29:02.561 align:middle line:90%


00:29:02.561 --> 00:29:08.060 align:middle line:84%
An area in the village where
you can rent a very cheap house.

00:29:08.060 --> 00:29:10.300 align:middle line:90%
I thought, can I live there?

00:29:10.300 --> 00:29:11.600 align:middle line:90%
Of course I can live there.

00:29:11.600 --> 00:29:12.400 align:middle line:90%
Why not?

00:29:12.400 --> 00:29:15.700 align:middle line:84%
It's a roof, it's a
house, I can live there.

00:29:15.700 --> 00:29:17.170 align:middle line:90%
And I knew I can handle this.

00:29:17.170 --> 00:29:20.290 align:middle line:84%
Whatever will
happen, we will live.

00:29:20.290 --> 00:29:22.180 align:middle line:84%
>>And there's an
old Sioux saying

00:29:22.180 --> 00:29:26.610 align:middle line:84%
that says, the longest journey
you will make in your life

00:29:26.610 --> 00:29:30.480 align:middle line:90%
is from your head to your heart.

00:29:30.480 --> 00:29:36.870 align:middle line:84%
And this isn't because
we're stupid or we're slow.

00:29:36.870 --> 00:29:41.040 align:middle line:90%
It's because it takes time.

00:29:41.040 --> 00:29:43.830 align:middle line:84%
Before I had cancer, I
believed in the heart

00:29:43.830 --> 00:29:46.390 align:middle line:84%
but I was living
it from my head.

00:29:46.390 --> 00:29:51.470 align:middle line:84%
And that journey, like snow
melting into the ground,

00:29:51.470 --> 00:29:54.890 align:middle line:84%
the essence of my life
melted into my heart.

00:29:54.890 --> 00:29:59.060 align:middle line:84%
It took almost dying to make
that journey from my head

00:29:59.060 --> 00:30:02.380 align:middle line:90%
to my heart.

00:30:02.380 --> 00:30:05.230 align:middle line:84%
>>Your primary
intention needs to be

00:30:05.230 --> 00:30:09.970 align:middle line:84%
connectedness with the
heart at this moment.

00:30:09.970 --> 00:30:14.380 align:middle line:84%
>>I have to act from a
place of good intention.

00:30:14.380 --> 00:30:17.710 align:middle line:84%
A place of love
and kindness that

00:30:17.710 --> 00:30:20.740 align:middle line:84%
will allow me to
walk in this world

00:30:20.740 --> 00:30:23.590 align:middle line:90%
without creating any damage.

00:30:23.590 --> 00:30:26.920 align:middle line:84%
>>You may intend to
have a million dollars,

00:30:26.920 --> 00:30:32.603 align:middle line:84%
and that intention then
needs you to rob a bank.

00:30:32.603 --> 00:30:36.270 align:middle line:90%


00:30:36.270 --> 00:30:40.200 align:middle line:84%
If you really want the thing,
go to the heart and say,

00:30:40.200 --> 00:30:42.110 align:middle line:90%
this is what I want.

00:30:42.110 --> 00:30:45.360 align:middle line:84%
And the heart can say, I'll
show you how you get it.

00:30:45.360 --> 00:30:49.980 align:middle line:84%
You must be willing to work,
now, and trust me, now.

00:30:49.980 --> 00:30:53.040 align:middle line:90%
And then you can have it, yes.

00:30:53.040 --> 00:30:55.650 align:middle line:84%
If it's not going
to hurt anyone else.

00:30:55.650 --> 00:30:58.240 align:middle line:84%
>>Suppose you meet
someone who says,

00:30:58.240 --> 00:30:59.820 align:middle line:90%
I intend to make more money.

00:30:59.820 --> 00:31:02.400 align:middle line:84%
And he says, that's
my intention.

00:31:02.400 --> 00:31:06.190 align:middle line:84%
You can ask him, why do you
want to make more money?

00:31:06.190 --> 00:31:10.350 align:middle line:84%
And then you'll start to
learn some interesting things.

00:31:10.350 --> 00:31:13.110 align:middle line:84%
>>If making money becomes
your primary goal,

00:31:13.110 --> 00:31:16.260 align:middle line:84%
then know that you
