00:31:16.260 --> 00:31:18.420 align:middle line:84%
with the deepest
dimension in yourself

00:31:18.420 --> 00:31:21.180 align:middle line:90%
that we call the heart.

00:31:21.180 --> 00:31:25.680 align:middle line:84%
And even if you achieve your
goal and make a lot of money,

00:31:25.680 --> 00:31:28.890 align:middle line:84%
you will find that
ultimately it leads

00:31:28.890 --> 00:31:32.190 align:middle line:90%
to frustration and unhappiness.

00:31:32.190 --> 00:31:37.290 align:middle line:84%
>>Fulfill your dream, and
certainly money may come.

00:31:37.290 --> 00:31:42.030 align:middle line:84%
If money does not come, just
to have a life full of joy.

00:31:42.030 --> 00:31:44.100 align:middle line:84%
In my case, for
example, I never thought

00:31:44.100 --> 00:31:47.760 align:middle line:84%
I would make a living
out of writing.

00:31:47.760 --> 00:31:51.840 align:middle line:84%
I was writing because
I wanted to do it.

00:31:51.840 --> 00:31:53.640 align:middle line:90%
I had no choice.

00:31:53.640 --> 00:31:55.890 align:middle line:84%
So at the end of
the day, not only

00:31:55.890 --> 00:32:00.040 align:middle line:84%
I made money out of writing,
but I made a lot of money

00:32:00.040 --> 00:32:02.310 align:middle line:90%
out of writing.

00:32:02.310 --> 00:32:07.230 align:middle line:84%
>>It often happens that when
your actions become empowered

00:32:07.230 --> 00:32:13.800 align:middle line:84%
and contribute something
vital to this world,

00:32:13.800 --> 00:32:17.910 align:middle line:84%
then abundance in
some form-- and it

00:32:17.910 --> 00:32:22.710 align:middle line:84%
may be in the form of money--
can sometimes flow to you.

00:32:22.710 --> 00:32:24.630 align:middle line:90%
>>It was a great success.

00:32:24.630 --> 00:32:27.950 align:middle line:84%
Holland wanted this
magazine so it could grow,

00:32:27.950 --> 00:32:30.600 align:middle line:84%
