magazine of the Netherlands.

00:32:30.600 --> 00:32:31.750 align:middle line:90%
It came from the heart.

00:32:31.750 --> 00:32:34.200 align:middle line:90%
It was the real thing.

00:32:34.200 --> 00:32:40.110 align:middle line:84%
>>Wherever your heart is, there
you will find your treasure.

00:32:40.110 --> 00:32:45.050 align:middle line:90%
>>The heart is who you are.

00:32:45.050 --> 00:32:49.410 align:middle line:90%
The heart defines you.

00:32:49.410 --> 00:32:55.900 align:middle line:84%
And I really wanted
to meet that person,

00:32:55.900 --> 00:33:00.860 align:middle line:84%
because I knew that person had
to be pretty special to get

00:33:00.860 --> 00:33:03.410 align:middle line:90%
Christina's heart.

00:33:03.410 --> 00:33:07.760 align:middle line:84%
Late one evening, my son got
a text message from a friend,

00:33:07.760 --> 00:33:11.300 align:middle line:84%
and said, tell your mom
to read the Facebook page.

00:33:11.300 --> 00:33:14.000 align:middle line:84%
So I went to Facebook,
and I saw a message.

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:17.090 align:middle line:84%
And the message was,
I am Susan Vieira,

00:33:17.090 --> 00:33:20.330 align:middle line:84%
and I believe I'm the recipient
of your daughter's heart.

00:33:20.330 --> 00:33:24.740 align:middle line:84%
I knew it was late, but I just
figured I'd message her anyway.

00:33:24.740 --> 00:33:27.100 align:middle line:90%
And she responded right back.

00:33:27.100 --> 00:33:32.431 align:middle line:84%
And I dialed her number,
and she picked up.

00:33:32.431 --> 00:33:34.780 align:middle line:84%
And right away I just
felt a connection.

00:33:34.780 --> 00:33:38.084 align:middle line:90%


00:33:38.084 --> 00:33:41.400 align:middle line:90%
I felt Christina.

00:33:41.400 --> 00:33:44.850 align:middle line:84%
And then when I heard this
she was a retired nurse,

00:33:44.850 --> 00:33:47.660 align:middle line:84%
and that they had
so much in common,

00:33:47.660 --> 00:33:51.530 align:middle line:84%
that it was like
Christina handpicked Susan

00:33:51.530 --> 00:33:53.090 align:middle line:90%
to get her heart.

00:33:53.090 --> 00:33:56.300 align:middle line:10%
>>Christina and I
