>>I'm going to have to
wait a while on that one.

00:34:30.550 --> 00:34:31.460 align:middle line:90%
>>Ride a camel.

00:34:31.460 --> 00:34:32.260 align:middle line:90%
>>Done that.

00:34:32.260 --> 00:34:34.040 align:middle line:90%
>>Travel to all the continents.

00:34:34.040 --> 00:34:35.000 align:middle line:90%
>>Working on it.

00:34:35.000 --> 00:34:36.980 align:middle line:84%
>>Be remembered as
the smiley girl.

00:34:36.980 --> 00:34:39.080 align:middle line:84%
>>I'm still working
