01:14:28.030 --> 01:14:30.740 align:middle line:90%
to kill every Tutsi that night.

01:14:30.740 --> 01:14:35.470 align:middle line:84%
And we were, our
family, on the list.

01:14:35.470 --> 01:14:38.382 align:middle line:84%
>>I cannot move the family
just because you heard a rumor.

01:14:38.382 --> 01:14:40.090 align:middle line:84%
>>What if it's true,
and in the morning--

01:14:40.090 --> 01:14:40.900 align:middle line:90%
>>Stop it.

01:14:40.900 --> 01:14:41.700 align:middle line:90%
No fear.

01:14:41.700 --> 01:14:44.085 align:middle line:84%
Just trust in God
and forget about it.

01:14:44.085 --> 01:14:47.410 align:middle line:90%


01:14:47.410 --> 01:14:48.580 align:middle line:90%
What do you think?

01:14:48.580 --> 01:14:49.810 align:middle line:90%
>>We should move.

01:14:49.810 --> 01:14:52.040 align:middle line:90%
This is so important.

01:14:52.040 --> 01:14:54.040 align:middle line:84%
