can just take the boat,

01:14:54.040 --> 01:14:55.910 align:middle line:84%
and come back in the
morning if nothing.

01:14:55.910 --> 01:14:59.440 align:middle line:84%
>>I know, but we must
trust our father, too.

01:14:59.440 --> 01:15:00.790 align:middle line:90%
>>I know, you're right.

01:15:00.790 --> 01:15:03.310 align:middle line:90%
We should, right?

01:15:03.310 --> 01:15:05.530 align:middle line:84%
>>Because he always
has good judgment.

01:15:05.530 --> 01:15:08.160 align:middle line:90%
>>We should.

01:15:08.160 --> 01:15:13.140 align:middle line:84%
>>It was so clear in my
heart that my decision was

01:15:13.140 --> 01:15:15.270 align:middle line:90%
to move away from the country.

01:15:15.270 --> 01:15:18.280 align:middle line:90%
By the morning, it was too late.

01:15:18.280 --> 01:15:22.050 align:middle line:84%
They had blocked
all the borders.

01:15:22.050 --> 01:15:26.370 align:middle line:84%
That lesson completely
changed my heart forever.

01:15:26.370 --> 01:15:30.090 align:middle line:84%
Now when I have that feeling,
I do listen to my heart,

01:15:30.090 --> 01:15:31.890 align:middle line:90%
no matter who is saying what.

01:15:31.890 --> 01:15:34.960 align:middle line:90%
I have to listen to my heart.

01:15:34.960 --> 01:15:36.540 align:middle line:84%
>>Well, if you don't
trust the heart,

01:15:36.540 --> 01:15:38.260 align:middle line:90%
what are you going to trust?

01:15:38.260 --> 01:15:45.600 align:middle line:84%
>>I believe the heart is
the only thing we can trust.

01:15:45.600 --> 01:15:48.420 align:middle line:84%
>>When we get to the point
where we have experienced

01:15:48.420 --> 01:15:51.900 align:middle line:84%
this transformation
within ourselves, where

01:15:51.900 --> 01:15:54.300 align:middle line:84%
living from love
rather than fear

01:15:54.300 --> 01:15:57.510 align:middle line:84%
has transformed our
own life circumstances,

01:15:57.510 --> 01:15:59.730 align:middle line:84%
then we become channels,
we become vessels.

01:15:59.730 --> 01:16:02.010 align:middle line:84%
We have the moral
authority by which

01:16:02.010 --> 01:16:04.380 align:middle line:84%
to state that possibility
for the planet.

01:16:04.380 --> 01:16:07.020 align:middle line:84%
>>Just before she
passed, I was telling her

01:16:07.020 --> 01:16:10.980 align:middle line:84%
that I'd been off work
for a couple of years,

01:16:10.980 --> 01:16:12.480 align:middle line:90%
and we retired.

01:16:12.480 --> 01:16:15.150 align:middle line:84%
And I was kind of
looking for something

01:16:15.150 --> 01:16:17.730 align:middle line:84%
meaningful to do with
the rest of my life,

01:16:17.730 --> 01:16:19.980 align:middle line:90%
because I was still young.

01:16:19.980 --> 01:16:23.060 align:middle line:84%
And she said, oh,
something will come along.

01:16:23.060 --> 01:16:27.480 align:middle line:84%
You'll know it when
it comes along.

01:16:27.480 --> 01:16:30.270 align:middle line:84%
And when she passed,
I knew instantly

01:16:30.270 --> 01:16:32.010 align:middle line:84%
that we had to
continue her work.

01:16:32.010 --> 01:16:34.180 align:middle line:10%
And so we started the
foundation, the Christina

01:16:34.180 --> 01:16:38.760 align:middle line:10%
Chesterman Memorial Foundation,
to just build on the legacy

01:16:38.760 --> 01:16:40.900 align:middle line:10%
that she left already.

01:16:40.900 --> 01:16:43.350 align:middle line:84%
>>As you live from the
heart and more humans

01:16:43.350 --> 01:16:48.510 align:middle line:84%
begin to live from the heart,
that has a ripple effect.

01:16:48.510 --> 01:16:53.280 align:middle line:84%
It ripples out from where you
are, and then you get it back.

01:16:53.280 --> 01:16:55.380 align:middle line:90%
>>Every day you work at it.

01:16:55.380 --> 01:16:57.450 align:middle line:90%
Every day you go to the heart.

01:16:57.450 --> 01:17:00.120 align:middle line:90%
Every day you speak to me.

01:17:00.120 --> 01:17:02.340 align:middle line:84%
>>In fact, I start
each morning with what

01:17:02.340 --> 01:17:03.600 align:middle line:90%
we call a heart lock in.

01:17:03.600 --> 01:17:06.900 align:middle line:84%
Just getting coherent
and really sending myself

01:17:06.900 --> 01:17:08.850 align:middle line:84%
love and appreciation
for a few minutes,

01:17:08.850 --> 01:17:11.640 align:middle line:84%
to start my day from
a more coherent,

01:17:11.640 --> 01:17:15.080 align:middle line:84%
composed, and
connected perspective.

01:17:15.080 --> 01:17:18.450 align:middle line:84%
Then throughout the day you've
got to kind of reboot that.

01:17:18.450 --> 01:17:22.710 align:middle line:84%
So really it's developing
kind of a flow through life.

01:17:22.710 --> 01:17:24.960 align:middle line:84%
So all the in-between
moments, as I call them.

01:17:24.960 --> 01:17:27.330 align:middle line:84%
Like in between here
and the lunch room,

01:17:27.330 --> 01:17:29.970 align:middle line:84%
or between here and
the photocopier.

01:17:29.970 --> 01:17:33.220 align:middle line:84%
Those in-between moments
are perfect opportunities

01:17:33.220 --> 01:17:37.974 align:middle line:84%
to breathe in that appreciation,
or that state of inner ease.

01:17:37.974 --> 01:17:39.390 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we have
to breathe anyway,

01:17:39.390 --> 01:17:42.330 align:middle line:84%
so we might as well
make it more effective.

01:17:42.330 --> 01:17:46.680 align:middle line:84%
>>And if we can
calm down enough,

01:17:46.680 --> 01:17:49.590 align:middle line:90%
we can listen to the wisdom.

01:17:49.590 --> 01:17:55.060 align:middle line:84%
We learn how to be good
neighbors, good visitors.

01:17:55.060 --> 01:17:57.136 align:middle line:90%
How to be good parents.

01:17:57.136 --> 01:18:01.660 align:middle line:84%
How to be good
workers, good teachers.

01:18:01.660 --> 01:18:06.022 align:middle line:84%
We learn how to
be good citizens.

01:18:06.022 --> 01:18:08.402 align:middle line:90%
Good human beings.

01:18:08.402 --> 01:18:12.210 align:middle line:90%
Because we listen.

01:18:12.210 --> 01:18:15.370 align:middle line:84%
And not try to put
our voices in it.

01:18:15.370 --> 01:18:16.750 align:middle line:90%
Just listen.

01:18:16.750 --> 01:18:18.100 align:middle line:90%
>>The heart is my guru.

01:18:18.100 --> 01:18:21.910 align:middle line:84%
For all gurus I've met,
this one is the real one.

01:18:21.910 --> 01:18:24.380 align:middle line:90%
>>Ask your heart any question.

01:18:24.380 --> 01:18:25.480 align:middle line:90%
Who am I?

01:18:25.480 --> 01:18:26.480 align:middle line:90%
What do I want?

01:18:26.480 --> 01:18:28.570 align:middle line:90%
What's my purpose in life?

01:18:28.570 --> 01:18:32.770 align:middle line:84%
What are the qualities that
I look for in a good friend?

01:18:32.770 --> 01:18:35.580 align:middle line:84%
What are the qualities
that I contribute to

01:18:35.580 --> 01:18:37.630 align:middle line:90%
in a good relationship?

01:18:37.630 --> 01:18:40.580 align:middle line:84%
What are my unique
skills and talents?

01:18:40.580 --> 01:18:42.640 align:middle line:84%
How do I use this
to serve humanity?

01:18:42.640 --> 01:18:44.628 align:middle line:84%
Your heart knows
all the answers.

01:18:44.628 --> 01:18:50.946 align:middle line:90%


01:18:50.946 --> 01:18:52.510 align:middle line:90%
>>I still feel lost.

01:18:52.510 --> 01:18:55.690 align:middle line:90%


01:18:55.690 --> 01:18:57.990 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what to do
with my life anymore.

01:18:57.990 --> 01:18:59.935 align:middle line:84%
>>Take the question
to your heart.

01:18:59.935 --> 01:19:02.310 align:middle line:90%
>>I have been.

01:19:02.310 --> 01:19:04.720 align:middle line:90%
I'm not getting any answers.

01:19:04.720 --> 01:19:08.280 align:middle line:84%
>>You're thinking, it's
harder than it really is.

01:19:08.280 --> 01:19:11.490 align:middle line:84%
Just follow that
lightness in your heart,

01:19:11.490 --> 01:19:15.600 align:middle line:84%
and that will eventually lead
you to a life of purpose.

01:19:15.600 --> 01:19:20.380 align:middle line:84%
Some of the biggest questions
of the heart unfold as a path,

01:19:20.380 --> 01:19:21.180 align:middle line:90%
not an answer.

01:19:21.180 --> 01:19:26.200 align:middle line:90%


01:19:26.200 --> 01:19:29.880 align:middle line:10%
>>Following our aliveness
without attaching

01:19:29.880 --> 01:19:32.670 align:middle line:10%
what it will become.

01:19:32.670 --> 01:19:37.480 align:middle line:84%
Not to become a poet,
but I'm brought alive

01:19:37.480 --> 01:19:43.170 align:middle line:84%
by the questions and
the life of expression.

01:19:43.170 --> 01:19:48.140 align:middle line:84%
Not to become a singer,
but to be brought alive

01:19:48.140 --> 01:19:51.700 align:middle line:90%
by voice coming out of you.

01:19:51.700 --> 01:19:55.860 align:middle line:84%
>>We begin to connect from
our center and not just

01:19:55.860 --> 01:19:58.250 align:middle line:90%
from surface personality.

01:19:58.250 --> 01:20:01.190 align:middle line:84%
It's a whole different way
of moving through the world.

01:20:01.190 --> 01:20:03.540 align:middle line:84%
And when one moves through
the world like this,

01:20:03.540 --> 01:20:06.620 align:middle line:84%
and when we begin to move
through the world like this,

01:20:06.620 --> 01:20:09.620 align:middle line:84%
then the realm of ever
expanding good-- another name

01:20:09.620 --> 01:20:12.996 align:middle line:84%
for heaven-- begins to be
revealed on our planet.

01:20:12.996 --> 01:20:16.350 align:middle line:90%


01:20:16.350 --> 01:20:22.020 align:middle line:84%
>>We cannot see tomorrow's
sky, but the heart sees it.

01:20:22.020 --> 01:20:24.660 align:middle line:84%
And we will be
directed as to how we

01:20:24.660 --> 01:20:28.650 align:middle line:90%
should act in tomorrow's sky.

01:20:28.650 --> 01:20:31.300 align:middle line:84%
More than likely,
we already know.

01:20:31.300 --> 01:20:35.070 align:middle line:84%
But if we don't, the heart
